-- Apache 
To check the version of apache
httpd -v 

Location of apache installation and key configuration file is httpd.conf
/etc/apache2/

Command to read apache configuration file and report any problem to it 
sudo apachectl configtest

/Library/WebServer/Documents/ contents the file that are displayed in a browser


-- PHP
location of php.ini file 
/private/etc/


-- MySQL

To uninstall MySQL copy all these command and run (make sure you stop the MySQL server before uninstalling)
sudo rm /usr/local/mysql
sudo rm -rf /usr/local/mysql*
sudo rm -rf /Library/StartupItems/MySQLCOM
sudo rm -rf /Library/PreferencePanes/My*
sudo rm -rf /Library/Receipts/mysql*
sudo rm -rf /Library/Receipts/MYSQL*
sudo rm /etc/my.cnf

-- Composer
Composer is installing in 
/usr/local/bin

Global composer.json is in 
/Users/dipak/.composer/composer.json

To update global composer packages
composer global update 

-- Drush
